Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的孩子们...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}My dear children...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迁居纽约已有多年\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}it is now better than several years since I moved to New York
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能如愿常见你们\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and I haven't seen you as much as I would like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你们前来观礼\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I hope you will come to this ceremony of papal honors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇圣谕褒奖我行善\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}given for my charitable work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽约 1979年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上唯有子女是财宝\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The only wealth in this world is children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人间财权难以比拟\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}More than all the money, power on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我的至宝\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}you are my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼 玛莉\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Anthony and Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你们能更好地成长\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}although I entrusted your education to your mother for your own best interests
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将你们托付给你们的母亲\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}you know how I look forward to seeing you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无时无刻都想和你们重聚天伦\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and to a new period of harmony in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你们能说动母亲来观礼\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Perhaps you might prevail upon your mother to come to this celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且时常参加家庭聚会\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and that from time to time we can all see each other at family functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你们如昔 父字\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Anyway, I remain, your loving father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万福玛利亚 满被圣宠者\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hail Mary, full of grace
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女中尔为赞美\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}blessed art Thou amongst women
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尔胎子耶稣并为赞美\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and blessed is the fruit of Thy womb,Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天主圣母玛利亚\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Holy Mary, mother of God
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我等罪人祈祷\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}pray for us sinners
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全能天主降福这圣萨巴辛徽章\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Almighty God, bless the insignia of Saint Sebastian the Martyr
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿徽章之神圣圣化受封人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}that it may contribute to the sacredness of him to whom it is given.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 你是否\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Do you, Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓忠于徽章崇高的宗旨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}promise to be faithful to the noble purposes of this order
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赈济贫穷 扶救疾苦\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}to have a special care for the poor, the needy and those who are ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承诺!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I do so promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿全能者天主圣父 圣子 圣神降福于你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}May the blessing of Almighty God Father, Son, and Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你同在以迨永远\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}descend upon you and remain with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿们!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森 名单上没有我们\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Vincent, our name's not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就写上去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Write it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼西尼 M-A-N-I-N-I\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Mancini. M-A-N-C-l-N-I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Is there a problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 名单上没有我的名字\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No problem, our name's not on the list. My name's not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请你马上离开 没有第二条路\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Then you have to leave immediately. No two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跳舞吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You want to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔 这是阿森 没关系 他们是客人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Joe, it's Vinnie. It's okay. These are our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对不起 大卫 - 没关系\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- I'm sorry, Dave. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿森 欢迎光临!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Vinnie, welcome to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你真高兴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 这是我丈夫\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's good to see you again. This is my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我儿子安东尼!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This is my son, Anthony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣萨巴辛勳章在教廷\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The order of Saint Sebastian is one of the highest honors
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是颁给凡人的最高荣誉\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}the Catholic Church can bestow upon a layman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它始于教皇格里哥利\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The award was first granted by Pope Gregory
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂先生与赌场的关系怎么办?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What about Mr. Corleone's connections with Las Vegas gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报道中有些照片...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Presskits have pictures of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有他和黑道的牵扯呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What about his involvement with the underworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少说废话\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Cut the crap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇今天亲自\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The pope, the Holy Father himself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐福麦克柯里昂\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}has this very day blessed Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你比教皇更懂?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You think you know better than the pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 文森! - 干嘛?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Vincent! - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爱你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}She loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以? 我也爱你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yeah? I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森 我记得你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hi Vincent. I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得我?在哪儿?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You remember me? From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我们一起参加的派对\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}From the last time when we were at a party together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前去过俱乐部?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Did you come down to the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是个婚礼\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No, it was a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我八岁 你十五岁时\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was 8; and you were 15
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十五岁时我女友一大票\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well I, I had a lot of girlfriends when I was 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八岁的女友?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}8 year olds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是八岁\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Especially 8 year olds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where's Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位叫玛莉一声? 不好意思 阁下\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Would somebody please hail Mary. Excuse me your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没给我问候吻呢 亲戚相见要相吻\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know? You haven't kissed me hello yet. Relatives always kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是亲戚吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh, now we're related?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的小堂妹\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm your little cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲是谁?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你个提示 他是意大利人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'll give you a hint: he's Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉 大家都在等你呢\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Mary, we've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住声音要低 嗯?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Remember, remember now, keep your voice low, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有笑容 别忘了笑\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And smile! Don't forget to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯氏基金会荣誉主席\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The honorary chairman of the Vito Corleone Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女玛莉柯里昂\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}My daughter, Mary Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我大概继承了我父亲爱演说的习惯\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Thanks; I think I inherited my father's love for speech making
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是这样的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But here it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯氏基金会在世界各国济贫\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The Vito Corleone Foundation helps the impoverished of every country
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资助艺术发展医学研究\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}gives grants to artists, funds medical research
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是致力于建设西西里岛\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and is particularly dedicated to the resurrection of Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔戴大主教\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Archbishop Gilday
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一亿美元\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}here is, $100,000,000
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表维多柯里昂\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}for the poor of Sicily
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献给西西里贫民\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}in the name of Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要只花在一处上!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Don't spend it all in one place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉 我真为你骄傲\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Mary, I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为西西里做出了伟大的贡献\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}you've done a wonderful thing for Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿钱用在有需要的人身上\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well, let's just hope the money gets to the people who need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿们!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的重头戏\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But the most important part
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强尼方亭!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Johnny Fontane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来这里我很高兴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm happy to be here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们同庆麦克柯里昂受封\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'd like you to join me in honoring Commendatore Michael Corleone.
