Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.24,0:46:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这基金会应该帮助所有人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This foundation is supposed to help all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.51,0:46:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这是宗旨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Of course. That's the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.94,0:46:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是合法的 玛莉\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This is legitimate, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.78,0:46:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证这是合法的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I swear this is legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.82,0:47:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 我希望这件事令我们更加亲密\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Dad, I want this to bring me closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.06,0:47:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会不惜一切\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I would burn in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.46,0:47:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护你的安全\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.18,0:47:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 你乘那辆 我跟麦克一道走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No, no. You go in the other car. I'll ride with Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.97,0:47:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与你家交情最深\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}As your family's oldest friend
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.80,0:47:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一向由我给你通风报信\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm always chosen to bring you messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.27,0:48:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾图贝洛阁下 请说!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Tell me, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.48,0:48:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前给那些老伙计赚的钱 他们很感激\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your old partners are grateful for the money you made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.95,0:48:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说他们都崇拜你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They worship you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.32,0:48:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在你抛弃了他们 这让他们很伤心\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But their hearts are broken because they think you abandoned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.26,0:48:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"屹立"的生意 他们也要入股\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They want to share your deal on Immobiliare
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.93,0:48:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还是一家人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}to be a family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.80,0:48:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能帮他们洗钱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It can purify their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.40,0:48:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我办不到\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.01,0:48:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"屹立"必须是桩合法生意\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Immobiliare must be legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.95,0:48:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 可是他们不高兴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I know. But they're unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.99,0:48:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.92,0:48:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己别无所求\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I ask nothing for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.89,0:48:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只盼着能怡养天年\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Only peace in my old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.26,0:48:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我得抚慰身边的人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But I must please the world around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.40,0:49:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 你爸通情达理\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Michael, your father was a reasonable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.04,0:49:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学学他吧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Learn from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.78,0:49:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从父亲那里学到许多\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I learned many things from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.68,0:49:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家见个面吧 老伙计\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Call a meeting, my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.12,0:49:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借此来解决我们的恩怨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}so there are no debts or grudges.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.52,0:49:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会解决所有的问题\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We will make the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.33,0:49:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一起\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.34,0:49:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗马 梵蒂冈
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.88,0:49:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天梵蒂冈宣称\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The Vatican announced today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.41,0:49:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇保禄六世已因病\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}that Pope Paul VI has canceled his Sunday blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.42,0:49:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取消周日祈福\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}due to ill health.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.42,0:49:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生要求卧床静养\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}His physician has ordered total bed rest
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.59,0:49:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时停止一切活动\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and cessation of all activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.03,0:50:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚举行了记者会\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They just had a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.24,0:50:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣布教皇病重\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They said the pope's condition is grave. gravissimo, they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.73,0:50:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次会议的目的在于批准\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The purpose of this meeting is to ratify
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.27,0:50:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽约各股东通过的动议\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}the motion passed by our shareholders in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.18,0:50:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Please
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.45,0:50:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本集团代表天主教友财团\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}our group represents a consortium of Catholic businessmen
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.15,0:50:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对柯氏掌权\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}against the Corleone control.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.85,0:50:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵蒂冈已经投赞成票\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The Vatican has cast its vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.32,0:51:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯氏集团也已控制了董事会\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The Corleone Group already controls the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.43,0:51:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根据拉特兰之约\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}According to the Lateran Treaty
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.33,0:51:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵蒂冈投的票必须在罗马\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}the Vatican's vote must be ratified
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.07,0:51:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由教皇亲自批准\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}here in Rome by the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.17,0:51:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇病重\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The pope is gravely ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.87,0:51:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他康复之前\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Until he recovers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.34,0:51:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无能为力\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I am powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.71,0:51:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那万一他一病不起呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What if he dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.92,0:51:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么套句美国俗话\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Then as you Americans say
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.15,0:51:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过往一切一笔勾消\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}All bets are off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.09,0:51:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 等一下\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Gentlemen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.39,0:51:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个短暂耽搁 仅此而已\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This is a brief delay, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.80,0:51:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大主教 各位先生\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your Excellency, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.47,0:51:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家一起祷告\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I advise you join us in our prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.07,0:51:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈求教皇早日康复\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}for the Holy Father's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.14,0:51:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就说好了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We had an agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.18,0:51:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场会议只是形式罢了 只是个形式\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This meeting was to be merely a formality. That's all it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.25,0:52:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 请坐下 - 我宁可站着 谁能回答我?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Please sit down. - I'd rather stand. Could someone answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.69,0:52:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们把自己逼到了这里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We have put ourselves on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.52,0:52:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"屹立"在欧洲根深蒂固\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The Immobiliare has its roots in the European tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.29,0:52:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位务必要了解\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Please try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.76,0:52:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.36,0:52:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解你们的卑鄙手段\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your tactics are despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.33,0:52:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话从柯里昂先生口中说出来 可真是个不小的罪名\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well, that's quite an indictment, coming from a Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.80,0:52:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.90,0:52:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别忘了你们现在是在梵蒂冈\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Remember you're in the Vatican. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.71,0:52:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底 想要什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.28,0:52:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以取得控制权\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yes. You will take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.35,0:52:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们非常推举你为船队掌舵\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We'll gladly put you at the helm of our little fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.49,0:52:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但所有船只的方向必须一致\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}but our ships must all sail in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.99,0:52:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.59,0:52:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道你能在我们的船上呆多久?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}who can say how long your stay with us will last?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.80,0:52:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是针对你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.10,0:52:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是生意场你了解的 教父\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's only business. You should know, Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.81,0:53:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.45,0:53:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要跟我做生意\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You want to do business with me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.32,0:53:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就跟你们做生意\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I will do business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.48,0:53:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们全是毒蛇\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Vipers, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.66,0:53:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群披着宗教外衣的伪善者\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We're back with the Borgias.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.46,0:53:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦克叔 - 安德鲁\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Uncle Michael. - Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.53,0:53:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你来了 能在这里见到你太好了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I heard you were here. It's so nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.33,0:53:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 文森 - 安德鲁 你好吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Vincent. - Andrew, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.47,0:53:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包家怎么了? 他们的时代早就结束了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What is this with the Borgias? Those days are over, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.25,0:53:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认得吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.95,0:53:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.88,0:53:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁科橄榄油\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Genco Olive Oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.79,0:53:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的祖父就是从这里开始的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That's where our grandfather got his start.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.75,0:53:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每周靠送货赚3美元\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}as a delivery boy making three bucks a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.12,0:53:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年后他拥有了这家公司\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Three years later, he owned the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.49,0:53:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国才有这种事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Only in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.69,0:53:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.73,0:53:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森 你最近躲到哪儿去了?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Vincenzo, where have you been hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.13,0:53:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你帮忙的时候\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You deserted us
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.73,0:53:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下我们不管\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}when we need your help so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.00,0:53:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我回来了 要我做什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well now I'm back, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.47,0:53:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉札萨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Get rid of Joe Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.94,0:54:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卖毒品给孩子们\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He sells drugs to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.74,0:54:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我年轻的时候还太平无事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}When I was a girl, it was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.67,0:54:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今老了反而不敢走夜路\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm an older woman, I'm afraid to walk the streets at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.98,0:54:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们大概在哪里?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where are they supposed to be at?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.48,0:54:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易 怎么回事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Lou, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.78,0:54:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经迟了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.72,0:54:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候让你失望过?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Have I ever let you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.85,0:54:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.19,0:54:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.35,0:54:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢你了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.79,0:54:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们愉快\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.03,0:54:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.47,0:54:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的邻居有些麻烦\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Neighborhood's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.00,0:54:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都这么照应你的邻居?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You're keeping your eye out for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.60,0:54:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.97,0:54:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.51,0:54:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后都照应你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}From now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.71,0:54:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在想念你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I missed you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.18,0:54:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想念你 小妹妹\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I missed you, too, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.78,0:54:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怀念以前大家一起成长的时光\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I missed growing up with all my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.78,0:54:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没认识你之前我就想念你了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I didn't know you, and I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.79,0:54:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得当年我们父亲的事吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Do you remember stories about our fathers, the old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.52,0:54:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得 你想知道些什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yeah. What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.20,0:55:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山尼大伯是怎么样的人?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What was Sonny like?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.23,0:55:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是城里的风头人物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He was the prince of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.00,0:55:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在我出生之前就死了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He died before I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.64,0:55:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我听过关于他的许多故事 他是个传奇\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But I heard a million stories. He was a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.47,0:55:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我爸爸呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What about my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.68,0:55:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个伟大的人物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A great man, your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.68,0:55:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个英雄 他拯救了整个家族\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He's a hero. He saved the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.92,0:55:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 文森 - 什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Vincent. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.69,0:55:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有没有杀自己的亲兄弟?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Did he kill his own brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.39,0:55:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.30,0:55:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那些传言都是谎话?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}So those are all lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.34,0:55:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是传言 知道吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Just stories, sweetheart. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.64,0:55:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.58,0:55:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.55,0:55:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴你在我身边\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm glad you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.15,0:55:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高兴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm glad you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.26,0:56:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂哥\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.07,0:56:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想把札萨也带上来 然后把他推下去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'd like to take Joey Zasa up for a ride in this and drop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.81,0:56:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,札萨算什么\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Joey Zasa is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.68,0:56:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个微不足道的小跑腿\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He's a small-time enforcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.08,0:56:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就吹吹牛 吓唬吓唬人 没什么\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He bluffs, threats, but nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.99,0:56:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老远你就能知道他来了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You'll be able to see him coming a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.32,0:56:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们应该趁早杀了他以免... - 不行!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- We should kill him before he kills... - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.06,0:56:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不要恨你的敌人 这会影响你的判断\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Never hate your enemies. It affects your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.71,0:56:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新泽西 亚特兰大城
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.62,0:57:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 柯里昂先生 很高兴再次见到你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Good evening. Nice to see you again, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.93,0:57:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信你 让你来掌管我们赌场的钱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We trusted you to manage our money in the casinos.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.33,0:57:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可还不到二十年 你就卖掉赌场\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's not even 20 years you sold the casinos
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.00,0:57:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我们大家都大赚了一笔\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and you made fortunes for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.24,0:57:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害啊柯里昂阁下!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Bravo, Don Corleone!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.84,0:57:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.81,0:58:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们 我到这里来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Friends, I have come here
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.45,0:58:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我们的共同事业已经结束了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}because, our business together is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.28,0:58:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都赚了大钱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We have prospered
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.05,0:58:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是时候\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and now it is time for us
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.19,0:58:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除我们之间的合作关系了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}to dissolve the business relationship between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.36,0:58:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.13,0:58:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我有份小礼物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But I do have a little surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.50,0:58:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位在赌场所持的股份\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your shares in the casino
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.34,0:58:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会免去所有程序\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I thought I'd cut through all the red tape
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.15,0:58:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接兑现\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}so you can get your money right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.68,0:58:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五千万!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}$50 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.25,0:58:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都不一样 按当初...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Not everybody gets the same. It depends on how much...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.05,0:58:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 没你的份儿 - 你资的额度及时间长短\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Nothing for you. - you invested and how long for.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.02,0:58:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 你真大方!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Michael, this is really generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.29,0:58:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.00,0:58:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Grazier
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.63,0:58:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴利西 你当初投了多少?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hey, Parisi, how much did you invest?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.74,0:58:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记不得了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.87,0:59:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝会保佑你的 麦克\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Michael, you're blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.41,0:59:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家族担了大部分苦差事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}My family has done much of the hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.98,0:59:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒了很多风险\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}taken many risks
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.35,0:59:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来为你们赚钱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}all to make money for the rest of the families.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.79,0:59:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都认识乔札萨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You all know Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.83,0:59:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认他是个大人物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He is, I admit, an important man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.33,0:59:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时代周刊封面登过他的照片\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}His picture is on the cover of the New York Times Magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.73,0:59:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绅士杂志还封他为最佳着装帮派人物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He gets the Esquire magazine award for the best-dressed gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.04,0:59:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各大报纸赞扬他 因为他雇用黑人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The newspapers praise him because he hires blacks into his family
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.24,0:59:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现得那么宽厚\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}which shows he has a good heart
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.11,0:59:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个名人 天知道\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He is famous. Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.35,0:59:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有一天\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Maybe one day
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.32,0:59:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会让在做各位都成为名人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}he will make all of you popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.46,0:59:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.73,1:00:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讲究穿着和仪容\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I make more of a bella figura.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.66,1:00:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的天性\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That is my nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.53,1:00:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也想让自己的事业合法化\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But I also want to make a move into legitimate enterprises.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.67,1:00:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要教皇给我封勋\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'd like to get a little pin from the pope.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.64,1:00:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 我雇佣黑人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Sure, I take the blacks
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.61,1:00:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是南美籍人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and the Spanish into my family
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.08,1:00:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是美国\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}because that's America.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.25,1:00:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢担保他们不在我们的地盘上贩毒?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And you guarantee that they don't deal drugs in those neighborhoods.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.36,1:00:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我不担保\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I don't guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.49,1:00:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只担保谁贩毒我杀谁\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I guarantee I'll kill anybody who does.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.73,1:00:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来劝劝他 我来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Let me talk to him. Let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.13,1:00:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能拒绝艾图贝洛阁下?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who can refuse Don Altobello?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.44,1:00:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Joe
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.84,1:00:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.51,1:00:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你们\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I say to all of you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.77,1:00:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 你们对我毫无尊重\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I have been treated this day with no respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.05,1:00:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你们所有人赚钱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I've earned you all money.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.18,1:00:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你们发财\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I've made you rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.05,1:00:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己只要求少许\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and I asked for little.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.55,1:00:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊你们不给?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Good. You will not give?
