Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.35,1:37:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最坚强的人也要交朋友\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Even the strongest man needs friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.39,1:37:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太荣幸了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.96,1:37:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但鲁西尼阁下你是金融政治人物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But you're a man of finance and politics, Don Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.90,1:37:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事我都不懂\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}these are things I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.13,1:37:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎么用枪吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You understand guns?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.50,1:37:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金融就是一把枪\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Finance is a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.97,1:37:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政治\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Politics
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.07,1:37:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是知道适时扣扳机\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}is knowing when to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.81,1:38:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做些什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.52,1:38:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求和平的人总是受到赐福\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Blessed is the peacemaker
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.36,1:38:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他可以被称为是神的儿子\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}for he can be called a child of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.49,1:38:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 懂说一点意大利语吗? - 懂\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Can you speak Italian well? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.88,1:38:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤马西诺阁下的轮椅\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The wheelchair, for Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.43,1:38:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笔交易我托给了大主教\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I trusted this business arrangement with the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.10,1:38:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么相信他 相信他的诚实\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I trusted him. I was sure his honesty was beyond a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.34,1:39:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在 我完全被骗了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But, as you see, I'm now the victim of a swindle.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.68,1:39:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在拖延着我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He's stalling me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.64,1:39:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨额的钱财都到了政界高层手里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Vast money have gone to the pezzonovante in high political places
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.75,1:39:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而梵蒂冈银行为其做担保人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and the Vatican Bank is the guarantor.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.72,1:39:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如过你说的话属实\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}If uh, what you say is true
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.39,1:39:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将是个大丑闻\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}there will be a great scandal.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.16,1:39:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这块石头\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Look at this stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.76,1:39:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它泡在水里已经很久了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It has been lying in the water for a very long time
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.16,1:39:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水却仍然没有能够浸透它\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}but the water has not penetrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.87,1:39:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.27,1:39:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是干的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Perfectly dry.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.11,1:39:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧洲人也是这样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The same thing has happened to men in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.75,1:39:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少个世纪以来 他们一直受基督教教诲\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}For centuries they have been surrounded by Christianity
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.65,1:39:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但基督却仍然没能进入他们的心里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}but Christ has not penetrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.45,1:39:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能与他们在生活中相伴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Christ doesn't breathe within them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.39,1:39:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.53,1:39:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能 给我点甜的东西?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Is it possible, that you could get me something sweet?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.93,1:40:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳橙汁 随便什么 糖果\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Orange juice, anything, candy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.04,1:40:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有糖尿病\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Trouble with diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.05,1:40:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血糖一定要保持低水平\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Blood sugar levels must be low.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.65,1:40:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.34,1:40:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力一大 有时候就这样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}When I'm under stress sometimes this happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.21,1:40:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.81,1:40:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来见你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I come to you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.18,1:40:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这种敏感的事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}on such a delicate matter
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.49,1:40:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指控大主教\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}accusations against your Archbishop
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.92,1:40:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言太难受\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}was difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.76,1:41:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神收到折磨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The mind suffers
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.03,1:41:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体自然不好\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and the body, cries out.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.70,1:41:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.21,1:41:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要做告解?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Would you like, to make your confession?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.05,1:41:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your Eminence
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.55,1:41:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 很久没有做告解了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm uh, I'm uh, it's been so long,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.33,1:41:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不 不 不知道从哪里...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I wouldn't, wouldn't, wouldn't know where to uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.83,1:41:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有三十年了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}it's been thirty years
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.20,1:41:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许会耽误你很久\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'd, I'd, I'd use up too much of your time, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.31,1:41:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救灵魂 我总是有时间的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I always have time to save souls.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.81,1:41:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 我已经罪无可赦\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well, I'm, I'm beyond redemption.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.49,1:42:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的教士也会向我告解\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I hear the confessions of my own priests here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.43,1:42:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候告解的心情已到极致\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Sometimes the desire to confess is overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.77,1:42:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要把握时机\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and we must seize the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.74,1:42:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我没有悔意\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What is the point of confessing
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.18,1:42:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告解有什么用?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}if I don't repent?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.01,1:42:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你精打细算\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I hear you are a practical man
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.48,1:42:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为告解会有什么损失吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What have you got to lose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.30,1:42:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.54,1:42:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.11,1:42:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对妻子不忠\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}betrayed my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.71,1:43:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说下去 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Go on, my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.95,1:43:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了自己的心\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I betrayed myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.66,1:43:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经杀过人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I killed men.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.36,1:43:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾令手下去杀人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And I ordered men to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.27,1:43:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着说 孩子 接着说\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Go on, my son, go on
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.67,1:43:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本没用\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.78,1:43:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Go on, my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.15,1:43:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I killed
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.35,1:43:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让人杀了我的兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I ordered the death of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.06,1:43:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他伤害了我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He injured me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.46,1:43:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了我母亲的儿子\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I killed my mother's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.36,1:43:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了自己的同胞兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I killed my mother's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.11,1:44:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的确罪大恶极\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your sins are terrible
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.48,1:44:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你身心遭受苦痛\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and it is just that you suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.28,1:44:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人生仍可获得救赎\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your life could be redeemed
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.82,1:44:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道你不相信\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}but I know that you don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.12,1:44:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不会有所改变\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You will not change.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.55,1:44:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇保禄六世\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Pope Paul VI
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.88,1:44:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗马天主教廷至尊\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}the Supreme Pontiff of the Roman Catholic Church
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.42,1:44:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于昨晚九时四十分辞世\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}died last night at 9:40pm
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.66,1:44:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享年八十一岁\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The Pope was 81 years old
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.77,1:45:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇在过去几个月一直受病痛折磨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and had been in poor health for the last several months
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.04,1:45:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康妮\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Connie
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.28,1:45:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这一辈子都在力争上游\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}all my life I, kept trying to go up in society
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.52,1:45:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望成为一个干净清白的人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}where everything higher up was legal, straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.26,1:45:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我爬得越高 世界就越险恶\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But the higher I go, the crookeder it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.53,1:45:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事什么时候才能结束?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}How in the hell does it end?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.87,1:45:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千百年来人类相互残杀\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Killing each other for centuries here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.58,1:45:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为钱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}For money
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.45,1:45:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为名 为家族\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}for pride, for family.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.92,1:45:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了免于沦为富贵者的奴隶\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}To keep from becoming the slaves of the rich pezzonovante.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.03,1:46:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了告解 康妮\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I made confession, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.17,1:46:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白了我的罪行\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I confessed my sins.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.90,1:46:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 麦克? 这可不像你的作风\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Why Michael, that's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.64,1:46:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必向一个陌生人坦白罪行\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You don't have to confess your sins to a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.14,1:46:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不一样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It was the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.85,1:46:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.15,1:46:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的神父\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A true priest.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.49,1:46:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可以改变事物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He changed things.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.99,1:46:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Michael
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.86,1:46:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}you know
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.83,1:46:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我会想起弗雷多\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}sometimes I think of poor Fredo
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.77,1:46:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淹死在湖里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}drowned.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.24,1:46:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是天意\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It was God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.57,1:46:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个可怕的意外\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It was a terrible accident.
