Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.73,1:48:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个麻烦?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Only one stone?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.83,1:48:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一个就很危险\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.54,1:48:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名鼎鼎的人物\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A famous man.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.67,1:49:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要格外小心\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You will have to take precautions.
