Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.79,1:49:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面包极品!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ah, what bread!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.69,1:49:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橄榄油\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ah, olive oil
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.10,1:49:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无杂味\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}virgin
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.70,1:49:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西西里独有\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}only in Sicily
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.24,1:49:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬你!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A salute!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.94,1:49:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬敌人!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A morte!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.73,1:49:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Kay!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.49,1:49:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康妮! 你好吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh, Connie! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.73,1:49:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉 好想你!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Mary, I've missed you!
