Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.50,1:50:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈 你看\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Mom, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.40,1:50:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"乡间骑士"
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.14,1:50:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜道格拉斯不能来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know it's too bad that Douglas couldn't be with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.41,1:50:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很想来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No, no, I know. He wanted to come very much,
