Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.35,1:50:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他一定想来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I know he wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.39,1:50:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 你儿子是个艺术家了 嗯?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well, your son's an artist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.46,1:50:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊应该谢谢你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh yes. Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.16,1:50:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh, what for?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.20,1:50:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢你逼我放他走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}For making me, let him go.
