Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.80,1:50:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}After all these years
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.30,1:50:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次来西西里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}here I am in Sicily for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.54,1:50:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你们照相\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I want to get a picture of you together.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.74,1:50:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 微笑\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hey dad, smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.98,1:50:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳利还在你身边 为什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I see you still have Al Neri. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.09,1:50:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要他啊他可以扶我上下车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well, I need him. He helps me get in and out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.79,1:51:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我提公事包\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Carry my briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.89,1:51:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在撒谎\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You're still a liar Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.00,1:51:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来带你看看真正的西西里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Let me show you Sicily. The real Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.50,1:51:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也许你能更了解我们家的历史\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Maybe you'll understand the family history a little better.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.10,1:51:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解的已经够多的了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh I think I understand it well enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.97,1:51:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Take them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.62,1:52:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Anthony
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.29,1:52:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多年前你做给我的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I have something you made for me a very long time ago
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.33,1:52:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会给你带来好运\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It may bring you luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.14,1:52:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留下来了?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You saved it, huh?
