Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.68,1:52:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Thank you dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.05,1:52:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为你骄傲\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.45,1:52:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.04,1:52:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的身手靠得住吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Are they as good as they look?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.20,1:52:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 一流高手\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They're better. They're the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.61,1:52:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他们在 麦克叔一定安全\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}As long as they're around, Uncle Michael is safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.24,1:53:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.38,1:53:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 告诉你爸我回来吃晚饭\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Bye. Tell your father I'll be back for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.02,1:53:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.85,1:53:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩儿的开心点\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.99,1:53:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉安东尼等我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And tell Tony to be sure to wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.69,1:53:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Okay. I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.52,1:53:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Bye mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.66,1:53:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 夫人 请吩咐\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Buon giorno, Signora. At your service
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.30,1:53:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到爸爸会告诉他你走了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}If I see dad, I'll tell him you left
