Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.45,1:53:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如麦克出事 我要你还击\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}If anything happens to Michael, I want you to strike back.
