Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.07,1:54:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲就是在这里出生\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Here it is. The house where my father was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.17,1:54:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们来到这里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This is where they came
