Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.85,1:54:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.32,1:54:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Listen to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.34,1:55:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉恋爱了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know, Mary's in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.84,1:55:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.71,1:55:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个黑眼睛的英俊意大利男人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}With a handsome young Italian man. Dark eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.02,1:55:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许这事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I won't allow it
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.52,1:55:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是错误的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.29,1:55:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错误而且危险\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's wrong and it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.73,1:55:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 我的父亲!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh father, my father!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.90,1:55:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一点时间向主祈祷\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Give me some time to pray to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.80,1:55:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡里尼男爵夫人不贞\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The Baroness of Carini had betrayed her husband
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.24,1:55:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同她的堂兄相恋\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and fallen in love with her cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.54,1:55:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There will be no forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.08,1:55:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她父亲举起宝剑\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Her father stabbed her
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.48,1:55:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将她一剑穿心!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}through the heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.69,1:56:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了家庭的名声吗\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Honor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.91,1:56:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得当年你去见我父母\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know, I remember the time that you came to my parent's house.
