Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.02,1:56:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那口气就像安东尼\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You sounded like Tony
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.66,1:56:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年的我的确很像\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was a lot like Tony.
