Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.84,1:56:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛有时侯还好 有时候就...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}My eyes. Sometimes they're all right. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.71,1:56:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我要去见汤马仙奴阁下\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Listen, I have to see Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.55,1:56:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 夫人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Benday, signora.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.22,1:57:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天没有随身保镖跟着啊\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There's no bodyguards today.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.19,1:57:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是真的偷跑出来的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I really snuck away.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.90,1:57:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父 上哪儿去? 要搭便车吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Father, where are you going? Would you like a ride?"
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.95,1:57:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认得你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.25,1:57:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是孟太利家的莫斯卡\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You're Mosca of Montelepre.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.95,1:57:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前当过杀手\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You were an assassin then
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.69,1:57:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and you're an assassin now
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.85,1:57:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道麦克·柯里昂在你家\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I know Michael Corleone is at your house.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.89,1:57:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟着你进去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I will pass through the gates with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.04,1:58:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡罗 你好吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.55,1:58:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是卡罗 我的老朋友\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Kay, this is Calo, my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.26,1:58:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的保镖\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}One of my bodyguards in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.86,1:58:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们可以在这里等他 - 要喝一杯吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- We can wait here. - You want drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.39,1:58:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我们进去?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yeah. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.86,1:58:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在这里度过了很长时间\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I spent a lot of time in this room
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.93,1:58:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想念你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.01,1:58:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你结婚了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And then you got married.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.91,1:58:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我依然想念你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I still thought of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.31,1:58:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那间房里有什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What's in that room?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.99,1:58:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 你知道来这里很危险\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know this is dangerous for you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.52,1:58:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿是西西里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This is Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.59,1:58:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱这里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I love this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.13,1:58:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.60,1:58:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世代以来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well, all through history
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.20,1:58:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人受尽折磨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}terrible things have happened to these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.47,1:59:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种不公正的事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Terrible injustice.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.77,1:59:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们依旧期待\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But they still expect good
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.88,1:59:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有好的事情发生\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}rather than bad will happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.18,1:59:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我和你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Sort of like me and you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.25,1:59:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}How so?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.35,1:59:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在这里啊\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well I'm still here, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.82,1:59:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的过去也不很愉快\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We do have a bad history
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.13,1:59:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还在这里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}but I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.36,1:59:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你还在 但是心里只有恐惧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh yes you are. But with dread.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.63,1:59:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出你的心意!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Gimme the order! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.97,1:59:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么做? 让我不怕你?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What's that supposed to do, is that supposed to make me not dread you?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.44,1:59:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来这里是为了看歌剧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We're in Sicily, the opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.18,1:59:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.08,1:59:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在干什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.79,1:59:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲道理\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.36,1:59:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我们不要再伤害彼此\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Let's try not to hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.33,2:00:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能原谅我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I want you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.24,2:00:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅你什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}For what?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.51,2:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.05,2:00:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像上帝那样?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh, like God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.85,2:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么夸张\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Oh, I, I need something a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.42,2:00:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时不了解我的处境\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You couldn't understand, back in those days.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.09,2:00:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱我的父亲\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I love my father
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.23,2:00:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经发誓不会成为他那样的人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I swore I would never be, a man like him
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.20,2:00:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我爱他 而他又身处险境\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}but I loved him. And he was in danger
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.00,2:00:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能怎么办?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.60,2:00:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 你也身处险境\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And then later, you were in danger.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.17,2:00:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子也一样 我能怎么办?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Our children, were in danger. what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.54,2:00:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我在这个世界上最重要的人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You were all that I loved, valued, most in the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.32,2:00:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我正在 已经失去了你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And, I'm losing you, I lost you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.59,2:00:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离开了我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You're gone.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.59,2:01:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了一切\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}and it was all for nothing
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.93,2:01:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}so
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.10,2:01:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要理解 我之后的人生都是注定的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}you have to understand, I had a whole different destiny planned.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.77,2:01:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我不说了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}All right, I'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.22,2:01:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 我不知道你到底要我怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I really don't konw what you want from me,Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.22,2:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.59,2:01:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I mean
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.39,2:01:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是你想像的那种人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm not the man that you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.56,2:01:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I dont't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.93,2:01:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 凯\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I love you, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.87,2:01:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再害怕我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Don't dread me, anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.74,2:01:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 在这里的每个晚上\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know, every night here in Sicily
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.72,2:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作梦\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I dream
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.79,2:02:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦见我的妻子和孩子\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}about my wife and my children.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.32,2:02:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦见我如何失去他们\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And how I lost them.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.43,2:02:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这对你是种安慰我想告诉你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I guess, if it's any consolation, I want you to know that
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.67,2:02:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 过去我一直爱你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I always loved you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.94,2:02:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后是一样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I always, I always will.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.11,2:03:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.05,2:03:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤马西诺阁下被人枪杀了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They found Don Tommasino shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.42,2:03:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.22,2:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家主人死了 血债血偿\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}My master is dead. Blood calls for blood.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.26,2:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要报仇\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I must have revenge
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.57,2:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来也许有难事要你去办\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Some day, you may have to do a difficult service for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.50,2:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管吩咐\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Command me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.14,2:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会为他报仇\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I will avenge him
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.43,2:03:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计票\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Totals
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.96,2:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗舒达 一票\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Lorscheider, 1 vote.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.27,2:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞里 十一票\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Siri, 11 votes.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.87,2:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙巴度 九十九票\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Lamberto, 99 votes.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.75,2:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否接受推举\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Do you accept your election
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.22,2:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任教皇圣职?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}as supreme pontiff?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.69,2:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝明鉴 赐福吾同僚之决策\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}My God, shed light on the decision they have taken on my behalf
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.06,2:04:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I accept.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.06,2:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望被如何称呼?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}By what name do you wish to be called?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.70,2:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若望保禄一世\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}John Paul the First.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:57.86,2:05:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将即刻执行此事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I will do things 'right away'
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.07,2:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不再考量拖延\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}rather than in 'a little while.'
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.30,2:05:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵蒂冈会计师凯斯济\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Frederik Keinszig, known for a decade as "God's banker,"
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.88,2:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已失踪三天 最后被见于\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}has been reported missing.He was last seen three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.74,2:05:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵蒂冈辖下\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}leaving the Rome offices of the Vatican owned
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.36,2:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"屹立"的罗马办公室内\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}corporation International Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.18,2:05:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随之失踪的还有大笔款项 及多份文件\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Also missing was a large sum of money, and several documents.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.05,2:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯济快接电话啊白痴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Come on, Keinszig, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.66,2:05:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯济的失踪\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Mr. Keinszig's absence
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.73,2:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得梵蒂冈银行的交易越显蹊跷\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}casts further suspicion on the dealings of the Vatican bank.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.73,2:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年以来该行及其下属子公司\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}For several years the bank and its subsidiary companies
